*Dokaza*o je da je njegov brat kriv za sve. (He proved that his brother was guilty for everything.)

Nisu imali *dokaza* da nastave s istragom. (They didn't have evidence to continue the investigation.)

On je naveo *dokaz*e o tome. (He presented evidence about that.)

Niste mogli da izbegnete njihove *dokaze*. (You couldn't avoid their proofs.)

Oni su imali *dokaz* da je ucenik kriv. (They had proof that the student was guilty.)